nodes.text: The Wanton Wellspring was a cantina located in the city Jibuto, on the planet Rajtiri. The Dressellian Has Obitt found the Wanton Wellspring no more inspiring than the Contented Krayt on Tatooine, or no more nastier than the Malicious Moondog on Suba. After the end of the Clone Wars, Obitt sat with a group of smugglers in the Wanton Wellspring shortly before they carried out a smuggling operation.
Following his stand against the Galactic Empire, Obitt received a hero's welcome at the Wellspring.
